<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Eder lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat der edel
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> Hadmar der <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> zu Laber, ewr sune,
                                <expan>jecz<ex>unden</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> als von <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan>
                        Gebels <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> wir vormals <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>bottsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> bey
                            <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex><ex>er</ex></expan> edel gehabt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Also <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <add><expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> zu</add>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>Fricze<ex>n</ex></expan> Strobel,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> diener, dem wir befolhen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, mit ewch davon zu reden, und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr edel mit
                            <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan> fleisz, was
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> unser diener von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu disem mal <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> an
                        ewch <expan>w<ex>er</ex>be</expan>, daz ir im das
                            <expan>genczl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gelawbe<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
                        darumb <expan>ausricht<ex>en</ex></expan> und von ewch
                                <expan>fertig<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet, als ir das vormals auch
                                <expan>gnedikl<ex>ich</ex></expan> getan habt und als wir zu
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel des ein gut getrawen
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. Das <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wir umb ewr edel etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                            <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>. </ab>
</div>
